<view class="page"><view class="page-title">{{itineraryId?'编辑行程':'新增行程'}}</view><view class="page-subtitle">先填写安排；还没决定时可以自然发起投票。</view><view class="section card pm-form-card"><view class="pm-field"><view class="pm-label">行程标题</view><input class="pm-input" value="{{form.title}}" data-k="title" bindinput="input" placeholder="例如：周六晚上晚餐"/></view><view class="pm-field"><view class="pm-label">行程类型</view><picker range="{{types}}" bindchange="pickType"><view class="pm-picker">{{form.itineraryType}}</view></picker></view><view class="pm-field"><view class="pm-label">日期</view><picker mode="date" value="{{form.itineraryDate}}" data-k="itineraryDate" bindchange="pickDate"><view class="pm-picker">{{form.itineraryDate}}</view></picker></view><switch checked="{{form.allDay}}" bindchange="toggleAllDay"/> <text class="muted">全天行程</text><block wx:if="{{!form.allDay}}"><view class="time-row"><picker mode="time" value="{{form.startTime}}" data-k="startTime" bindchange="pickDate"><view class="pm-picker">{{form.startTime||'开始时间'}}</view></picker><picker mode="time" value="{{form.endTime}}" data-k="endTime" bindchange="pickDate"><view class="pm-picker">{{form.endTime||'结束时间'}}</view></picker></view></block><view class="pm-field"><view class="pm-label">地点</view><input class="pm-input" value="{{form.locationName}}" data-k="locationName" bindinput="input" placeholder="地点名称"/></view><view class="pm-field"><view class="pm-label">地址</view><input class="pm-input" value="{{form.address}}" data-k="address" bindinput="input" placeholder="详细地址（可选）"/></view><view class="pm-field"><view class="pm-label">备注</view><textarea class="pm-textarea" value="{{form.description}}" data-k="description" bindinput="input" placeholder="补充说明（可选）"/></view></view><view wx:if="{{!itineraryId}}" class="section card poll-switch"><view><view class="section-title">还没决定？</view><view class="section-desc">发起投票，让大家一起确定安排。</view></view><view class="pm-link" bindtap="togglePoll">{{withPoll?'切回直接填写':'发起投票'}}</view></view><view wx:if="{{withPoll}}" class="section card pm-form-card"><view class="section-title">投票内容</view><view class="pm-field"><view class="pm-label">投票问题</view><input class="pm-input" value="{{poll.title}}" data-k="title" bindinput="pollInput" placeholder="例如：晚餐吃什么？"/></view><view wx:for="{{poll.options}}" wx:key="index" class="pm-field"><view class="pm-label">选项 {{index+1}}</view><input class="pm-input" value="{{item.optionText}}" data-i="{{index}}" bindinput="optionInput" placeholder="填写候选方案"/></view><view class="pm-link" bindtap="addOption">+ 新增选项</view></view><view class="pm-bottom-bar"><view class="pm-primary-action"><button class="pm-native-button primary" loading="{{saving}}" bindtap="save">{{withPoll?'保存并发起投票':'保存行程'}}</button></view></view></view>
